c: 7
v: 148
t: "Kananjalo abantu bakaMûsâ akungabikho (uMûsâ) bazenzela umfanekiso\t(oqingqiweyo)\twethole\tngezacholo\tzabo elalinesandi (elalisenza). Babengaboni na ukuba lalingekhe likwazi ukuthetha lingekhe libakhokele nokubakhokela eNdleleni ethe Tye? Balithatha (balinqula) lona baza baba ngabenzi bobubi"